Package edu.fhda.argos

Class Summary
ArgosV3Report The ArgosV3Report class collects all of the necessary elements need to successfully execute a report using Evisions Argos 3.x into one place.
 

Exception Summary
InvalidReportException Describes an error trying to validate the report object prior to either (a) execution, or (b) downloading the completed report file generated by Argos.
MAPSException Describes an error returned from the MAPS server including the HTTP status code, and the body of the response.
